Text: Do you think you could get more from R.L Mathewson please? I have Checkmate already. Please?
i uploaded the 3 books from "a neighbor from hell" series as part of my latest NYT Bestseller.

Ok, great, thank you. I just went through my book collection and wondered how I had this series. I read checkmate already and loved it! Now I know where they came from! Your collections are the greatest! Thanks again!!! :)
